  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Children 5-15 years old with a clinical diagnosis of appendicitis that prior to the
             trial would have been subjected to a surgical intervention

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Suspicion of perforated appendicitis on the basis of generalized peritonitis

          -  An appendiceal mass, diagnosed either by palpation or with radiology
      </textblock>
